text:
@zerohedge *LLM's masquerading as ai*

Truth is physical, and Bezo's is already throwing his weight behind developing an actual AI system. People all over the world are really, from Egypt to Canada. I'd wager China is. Maybe someone will tell an Indian too. 

Photonics will accelerate

