At the same time,", "id_str": "2065864078178873656", "in_reply_to_screen_name": "ohlelel", "in_reply_to_status_id_str": "2065864075918151873", "in_reply_to_user_id_str": "1721668428711235584", "is_quote_status": false, "lang": "en", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 1, "retweet_count": 0, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "1721668428711235584"}, "note_tweet": {"is_expandable": true, "note_tweet_results": {"result": {"entity_set": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [{"indices": [294, 299], "text": "AVGO"}, {"indices": [304, 309], "text": "MRVL"}], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNjU4NjQwNzgwOTkyMDYxNDQ=", "text": "That is also why I want exposure to both sides of the opportunity. I’m invested in photonics because I believe optical interconnects are becoming structurally more important as AI infrastructure scales and electrical interconnects approach practical limits. 

At the same time, I’m invested in $AVGO and $MRVL because they are positioned across the broader infrastructure spend happening today — custom silicon, switching, connectivity, and networking platforms that hyperscalers are already deploying."}}}, "rest_id": "2065864078178873656", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/iphone" rel="nofollow">Twitter for iPhone</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "61", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

